constraints.ocl:
context Airline
inv: self.code <> null implies self.name <> null

context Passenger
inv: self.email <> null implies self.passportNo <> null

context Aircraft
inv: self.seats->size() >= 1 and self.seats->size() <= 3

context Airline
inv: self.aircrafts->size() >= 1 and self.aircrafts->size() <= 2

context Airline
inv: self.flights->size() >= 1 and self.flights->size() <= 1

context Aircraft
inv: self.model.size() >= 10 implies self.model.substring(1, 10) = 'value'

context Flight
inv: self.bookings->size() >= 4 implies self.bookings->asSequence()->at(4).bookingRef <> null

context BoardingPass
inv: self.boardingTime <> null and self.gate <> null

context Passenger
inv: (self.email <> null and self.fullName <> null) or (self.email = null and self.fullName = null)

context Flight
inv: self.bookings->notEmpty() implies self.bookings->sortedBy(x | x.bookingRef)->first().bookingRef <= self.bookings->sortedBy(x | x.bookingRef)->last().bookingRef

context Booking
inv: self.baggages->notEmpty() implies self.baggages->sortedBy(x | x.tagNo)->first().tagNo <= self.baggages->sortedBy(x | x.tagNo)->last().tagNo

context Aircraft
inv: self.registrationNo.size() >= 5 implies self.registrationNo.substring(1, 5) = 'value'

context Booking
inv: self.baggages->size() >= 4 implies self.baggages->asSequence()->at(4).tagNo <> null

context Booking
inv: self.baggages->includesAll(self.baggages) or self.baggages->excludesAll(self.baggages)

context Flight
inv: self.departureTime <> '' and self.departureTime.size() > 0

context Flight
inv: self.departureTime <> null implies self.arrivalTime <> null

context Aircraft
inv: self.seats->notEmpty() implies self.seats->last().seatClass <> null

context Passenger
inv: self.bookings->notEmpty() implies self.bookings->first().createdAt <> null

context BoardingPass
inv: not(not(self.boardingTime <> null and self.gate <> null))

context Airport
inv: (self.departingFlights->size() >= 1 and self.departingFlights->size() <= 3) and (self.departingFlights->size() < 1)

context Flight
inv: not(self.departureTime <> null and self.arrivalTime <> null)
